# Contributing

By submitting a pull request, patch, issue comment containing code, or other contribution to this repository, you agree that your contribution is licensed under the same license as this project.

This project is licensed under the MIT License unless otherwise stated.

You certify that you wrote the contribution yourself, or that you have the legal right to submit it under this project's license.

Please do not submit code copied from another project unless you have the legal right to do so and the code is compatible with this repository's license.
